<plot>Guests follow a trail of pink and yellow wool around a garden until they find Pob, a "goblin baby" who wears a pink and yellow stripy jumper. The guests tell stories, etc. The show was a magazine programme for children, with items linked by Pob. The programme (in)famously featured Pob "misting" the screen while making raspberry-blowing noise, then writing his name "Puh, o', buh. Pob." in the "mist".</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?436552</url></doc>
